stats¶

generate_data(info: List[tuple])¶

Generates randomly sampled integer sets based on the parameters of info

Parameters

info – List of tuples. tup[0] is the range of values, tup[1] is the number of sampled values from that range

Returns

List of lists, each list being a sample
